  "detailed_description": "<strong>butterfly effect</strong> - <i>(noun)</i> - (with reference to chaos theory) the phenomenon whereby a minute localized change in a complex system can have large effects elsewhere.<br><br><strong>Surely one change shouldn't change everything, right?</strong><br><br>Play through this thrilling, story-based, psychological horror game, about small inconveniences that you must overcome, by dreaming that something was slightly different. Surely that shouldn't break the whole world and universe...",
